  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK176">
<l>aruḷveḵki yāṟṟiṉka ṇiṉṟāṉ poruḷveḵkip</l>
<l>pollāta cūḻak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If he, who through desire of the virtue of kindness abides in the domestic state i.e., the path in which it may be obtained, covet (the property of others) and think of evil methods (to obtain it), he will perish.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
